---
title: French Onion & Kale Soup with Gruyere Croutons
description: French onion soup gets its flavor from deeply caramelized onions. Achieving full caramelization is the key to greatness!  Our version has two secret ingredients: soy sauce and thyme for umami and depth. Of course, it’s not French onion soup without a gooey, cheesy crouton on top.
